snippet.title: It's Okay To Be Smart
snippet.description:
It's Okay to be Smart is created by Joe Hanson, Ph.D. 

We are all curious groups of atoms in a very curious universe. Join me as we explore curiosity together and illuminate the science behind everything. 

Have ideas or questions? Find me on Twitter: @okaytobesmart or @DrJoeHanson
